strings: <voice_0x0100130C><se_low>King of tricks: We finally got to Orkutsk.
<voice_0x0100130D><se_low>King of tricks: And that corner lawn is so nice! It doesn't get cold even when it snows!
<voice_0x0100130E><se_low>King of tricks: You can stay as long as you like. I will always be waiting for you on this earth!
